Product name: Rocky Alpha Force Zipper Waterproof Duty Boot
Description:
These hard-wearing Rocky® AlphaForce Waterproof Duty Black Boots are made with black full-grain leather and 1000-denier nylon fabric. Rocky AlphaForce boots are great EMT of occupational boots for tough work boot job needs. These lightweight, strong fabrics hold up even in the most extreme working conditions.

These duty boots have been built with Rocky Waterproof construction; this creates a barrier that is guaranteed to keep water out, so your feet will remain completely dry.

The Air-Port footbed is made from polyurethane and absorbs shock, but always reverts back to its earliest shape. The cushion footbed specifically targets your heel and metatarsal ridge, giving you support and comfort.

This boot features a non-metallic stabilizer, and has a non-marking RigiTrac outsole that provides oil and slip resistance.

A side zipper makes it easy to get these boots on and off quickly.

Whether you're looking for durable black work boots, tactical boots, a great pair of waterproof boots or superior law enforcement boots... These Rocky AlphaForce boots are the right choice to help you get the job done!

Product name: PolyTac HP
Description:
The PolyTac HP delivers bright light with a 275m beam distance for down-range illumination. It features a superior grip texture for a comfortable but slip-resistant feel, as well as TEN-TAP® Programming that gives users the choice of three operating modes.

  • C4® LED technology within a deep reflector provides far-reaching targeting beam with a tight spotlight and optimum peripheral illumination
  • TEN-TAP® Programming: Choice of three operating modes:
    1.) high/strobe/low (factory default); 2.) high only; 3.) low/high:
    • High for a super-bright, far-reaching beam: 275 lumens; 19,000 candela; 275m beam distance; runs 3 hours
    • Low for when less light is needed and for longer run times: 14 lumens; 1,000 candela; runs 56 hours
    • Strobe runs 5.5 hours
  • Solid State power regulation provides maximum light output throughout battery life
  • Deep reflector produces 275m beam - ideal for lighting the way to the end of a dark alley, down a wooded path, inspecting utility lines from the ground, or search and rescue missions
  • High-impact, super-tough nylon polymer for exceptional durability and a superior grip texture to provide a comfortable but slip resistant feel
  • IPX7 rated design; waterproof to 1 meter for 30 minutes
  • Powered by two 3V CR123A lithium batteries (included)
  • 5.90 in. (14.98 cm); 5.2 oz (148 grams) with batteries

Product name: Coast RX311 Rapid Response Blade Assist Folding Knife
Description: The Coast RX311 features blade assist technology which was designed by world class custom knife maker and inventor, Ron Lake. It uses a patented system using a roller-bearing mounted to the blade and a leaf spring mounted between the handle liners resulting in a blade that releases faster, smoother and safer than other assisted opening knives on the market. A stainless steel frame and nylon filled nylon handle add incredible strength and durability. Thumb studs on both sides of the blade and thumb ramping on both sides of the handle make firing the blade easy from right or left side carry positions. A reversible, stainless steel pocket clip is included making the knife fully ambidextrous. The knife uses Coast's patented Max-Lock technology which provides a second lock system. This safeguard secures the blade closed when not in use and double locks the Liner-Lock when open, even if the Liner Lock is inadvertently dis-engaged. Backed by Coast's lifetime guarantee against defects in materials and workmanship.

Description:
If you want comfortable duty shoes, get the Rocky® AlphaForce work shoe. It's made with the extremely comfortable Air-Port footbed that provides cushioning and support. The polyurethane material used in its insole is known for its cushioning while not bottoming-out features. Some open-celled foams feel very comfortable to the initial touch, but tend to break down faster than a product made with polyurethane. Plus, it is extra thick in the heel contact area. This provides additional underfoot comfort to the wearer.

These oxfords also have a non-metallic stabilizer and a RigiTrac outsole provides traction and resists oils and slips. The shoes are made of full-grain black leather that's water resistant and lightweight, black 1000-Denier nylon that resists scuffs and abrasions.

Description:
When your job calls for US Postal-Approved, slip-resistant, Berry-Compliant (Made in USA) footwear, the Rocky® TMC Postal Approved Duty Boot is what you want. The black duty boot is made with full-grain leather that can be polished.

The men's boot also features a padded collar and padded leather tongue for comfort and to help keep out dirt and debris.

This comfortable duty boot has Rocky's exclusive, extra thick PU Rocky Air-Port footbed with Airflow design. This design helps to keep your feet cool and comfortable (even on the hottest of days) and provide cushion as you walk.

In addition, AEGIS Microbe Shield® is applied to the Air-Port footbed covering. This offers durable control of odor, mold, fungus and mildew within your boot.

And to keep you on your feet, this postal duty boot is slip- and oil-resistant.

Whether you're going into a civil service career for the first time, or have been delivering mail for 30 years, the Rocky 8-inch postal-approved duty boot is the right choice for you!

Product name: Peerless Model 730 Superlite Aluminum Handcuffs, Gray
Description:
Introducing the new Model 730C – Superlite chain link handcuff with gray ceramic finish. Weighing in at just 5.2 ounces the Model 730 is near half the weight of a typical standard chain link handcuff. The Superlite is designed to meet the demands of law enforcement professionals while making the job a little easier. The Model 730’s major components utilize aerospace grade aluminum, carbon steel and stainless steel. It also features steel swivels, steel chain links and spun rivet construction. The smooth single-strand action has 21 locking positions with a push pin double lock.The Model 730C Superlite is National Institute of Justice Standard 0307.01 certified. The Model 730C comes with a lifetime warranty for manufacturer defects.

• Double Locking
• Two Keys Supplied
• Made in USA

Product name: Men's Rocky Alpha Force Zipper Waterproof Duty Boot
Description:
These hard-wearing Rocky® AlphaForce Waterproof Duty Black Boots are made with black full-grain leather and 1000-denier nylon fabric. Rocky AlphaForce boots are great EMT of occupational boots for tough work boot job needs. These lightweight, strong fabrics hold up even in the most extreme working conditions.

These duty boots have been built with Rocky Waterproof construction; this creates a barrier that is guaranteed to keep water out, so your feet will remain completely dry.

The Air-Port footbed is made from polyurethane and absorbs shock, but always reverts back to its earliest shape. The cushion footbed specifically targets your heel and metatarsal ridge, giving you support and comfort.

This boot features a non-metallic stabilizer, and has a non-marking RigiTrac outsole that provides oil and slip resistance.

A side zipper makes it easy to get these boots on and off quickly.

Whether you're looking for durable black work boots, tactical boots, a great pair of waterproof boots or superior law enforcement boots... These Rocky AlphaForce boots are the right choice to help you get the job done!

Product name: Men's Rocky TMC Postal Approved Duty Boot
Description:
When your job calls for US Postal-Approved, slip-resistant, Berry-Compliant (Made in USA) footwear, the Rocky® TMC Postal Approved Duty Boot is what you want. The black duty boot is made with full-grain leather that can be polished.

The men's boot also features a padded collar and padded leather tongue for comfort and to help keep out dirt and debris.

This comfortable duty boot has Rocky's exclusive, extra thick PU Rocky Air-Port footbed with Airflow design. This design helps to keep your feet cool and comfortable (even on the hottest of days) and provide cushion as you walk.

In addition, AEGIS Microbe Shield® is applied to the Air-Port footbed covering. This offers durable control of odor, mold, fungus and mildew within your boot.

And to keep you on your feet, this postal duty boot is slip- and oil-resistant.

Whether you're going into a civil service career for the first time, or have been delivering mail for 30 years, the Rocky 8-inch postal-approved duty boot is the right choice for you!

  • Made in the USA, Berry Compliant
  • Non-metallic stabilizer
  • Aegis Microbe Shield Applied to Rocky® Air-Port cushion footbed
  • Slip and Oil Resistant TMC Direct Attach TPU/PU outsole for Stability and Flexibility
  • Full-grain polishable leather
  • S.R. USA Postal Approved
  • 8 Inches in height

Product name: Men's Danner 8" Lookout Side Zip
Description: To build the Lookout, we combined Danner’s legendary durability and support, with the unmatched comfort found in the all-new Danner Comfort System (DCS). This new duty offering delivers best-in-class durability, support, and cushioning right out of the box. It features a waterproof, polishable, full-grain leather and ripstop ballistic nylon upper that stands up to the job, and an all-new waterproof Danner Dry liner that pulls moisture away from the foot for all-season comfort. The cushioned comfort comes from a patent-pending, dual-density footbed, combining underfoot venting for maximum airflow and an Airthotic heel clip for support. A wider toe box allows for a more responsive fit, while the rugged outsole delivers outstanding traction and maneuverability.Pride of service comes in many forms. For us, it’s our dedication to creating a better product: to make it stronger, to make it lighter, to make it last. As we developed the Striker Torrent, we challenged ourselves to find the perfect balance between comfort and support, while ensuring that the new Striker would outlast its predecessor.

Product name: Elbeco Navy Soft Collar Job Shirt
Description:
Elbeco Navy Soft Collar Job Shirt

Back = 3M Scotchlite Line 1 = Lake Johanna Line 2 = Fire

Left Shoulder = Lake Johanna Fire Patch

Right Shoulder Top = White Reverse Field Flag

Right Shoulder Bottom = Lake Johanna Fire Medical Patch

Left Chest = Embroidered Silver Badge Logo

Right Chest = Embroidered Line 1 = Rank Line 2 = First Initial/Last Name

The Shield Job Shirt features a heavyweight cotton blended fleece and is as functional and durable as it is comfortable! Designed with two options, wearers have the choice between the Self Collar or the Twill Collar, providing a quarter front zipper closure with a chin guard that protects the chin and neck from the zipper. The lined Twill Collar is styled with fabric elbow patches that feature our Tek3 fabric for excellent match, color retention and nano fluid repellency technology. Additional benefits include mic pockets at shoulder seams, tab at center of chest for mic clip and sunglass options, dual fleece-lined side hand warmer pockets with internal storage pockets for cell phone and D-ring feature for carabiner/key security, and roomy chest pocket that accommodates a full-sized radio.

  • Fabric Features: 82% cotton/18% poly heavy weight fleece | Weight: 11.5 oz/sq yard
  • Self collar (3730) quarter front zipper closure with chin guard protects chin and neck from zipper
  • Lined twill collar (3732) and fabric elbow patches feature our Tek3 fabric for excellent match, color retention and nano fluid repellency
  • Dual fleece-lined side hand warmer pockets with internal storage pockets for cell phone and D-ring feature for carabiner/key security
  • Roomy chest pocket at the seam with hook and loop dividers to accommodate a full-sized radio or a smaller object without it dropping to the bottom of the pocket
  • Mic pockets at both shoulders and center tab at bottom of front zipper offering mic clip and sunglass options
  • Beefy ribbed waist and cuffs for shape retention
  • Pen pockets on left sleeve
  • Tall sizes available (T3730)

Product name: Game Navy Quilted Vest
Description:
Game Navy Quilted Vest


Left Chest = Badge Logo Embroidered in Silver

Right Chest = Embroidered Line 1 = Rank Line 2 = First Initial/Last Name in Silver

Game Sportswear’s cool, new Diamond Quilted Vest offers all the quality

and features of their popular Diamond Quilt Jacket, “The Bravest” —but

without the sleeves. You’ll find it exceptionally light weight,

comfortable, thermally efficient, and remarkably versatile. Wear it as a

stylish outer garment. It keeps your torso warm in moderately cold

weather; but leaves arms free for unrestricted movement, while allowing

excess body heat caused by exertion to radiate off through your arms. Or

in the coldest weather you can wear it as an extra insulated lining

under your outer jacket, for extra warmth without adding bulk around

your arms. To make your vest even more finished, and more personal,

consider adding one of our stock embroidered logos or personalized

custom embroidery."The Finest" will not only make your department more

comfortable…it will make them proud.

Features:

  • Water resistant nylon Tafetta shell
  • 5 oz. polyfill lining with thermal knit backing
  • 100% polyester rib knit collar
  • Full front metal zipper
  • 2 outer pockets
  • Machine washable

Product name: NAR-TQ Tourniquet
Description:
Noted as the best prehospital tourniquet in the February 2008 supplement of The Journal of Trauma

The patented C-A-T® is a true one-handed tourniquet proven to be 100% effective by the U.S. Army’s Institute of Surgical Research. Tests proved that the C-A-T® completely occluded blood flow of an extremity in the event of a traumatic wound with significant hemorrhage.

The C-A-T® utilizes a durable windlass system with a patented free-moving internal band providing true circumferential pressure to the extremity. Once adequately tightened, bleeding will cease and the windlass is locked into place. A hook and loop windlass retention strap is then applied, securing the windlass to maintain pressure during casualty evacuation. The C-A-T®’s unique dual securing system avoids the use of screws and clips which can become difficult to operate under survival stress or where fine motor skills are compromised.

The patented Combat Application Tourniquet® (C-A-T®) featuring the proprietary red tip design and the mechanical advantage of a band within a band has been the Official Tourniquet of the U.S. Army since 2005.

Product name: Blackhawk Epoch L3 Holster w/ TLR-1 & TLR-2
Description:
Building on our track record of reliable holster performance, the Epoch Holster delivers three levels of weapon retention for our highest level of security. The patent-pending retention system engages the pistol’s ejection port when holstered and won’t let go until you release it. As an added safety measure, the Pivot Guard opens by thumb activation and is designed so it won’t close accidentally, locking you out of the holster. This unique design accommodates the most popular under-barrel lights on the market today, giving you all the versatility you’ve come to expect from BLACKHAWK!®


• Passive retention detent screw

Product name: Rigid TQ Case For Tourniquet
Description:
The Eleven 10® RIGID TQ Case for the CAT Gen 7 is a hard-sided tourniquet case designed to give you easy access to your tourniquet when seconds matter. It can be worn on your duty belt, MOLLE/PALS compatible vest, or in the accessory position on your Safariland drop leg holster. The RIGID TQ Case holds your tourniquet securely in place utilizing friction, so there’s no straps, buckles or flaps to deal with. It offers true one-handed gross motor skills deployment of the tourniquet even when your hands are bloody or wet. Just grab the exposed portion of the tourniquet and with a swift pull, it releases.

Massive bleeding in an extremity can often be stopped using a tourniquet, but seconds can be the difference between life and death. Having your tourniquet in a RIGID TQ Case will ensure that you can access and deploy your tourniquet in seconds, and it will always be on your person.

The injection molded RIGID TQ Case offers numerous mounting options and ride adjustment. It’s compatible with Blade-Tech, Safariland, Tactical Tailor and Raven Concealment Systems mounting solutions. Many of the mounting solutions can be mounted in the vertical or horizontal positions.

  • Keeps your tourniquet close at hand for rapid deployment
  • Holds C-A-T® Tourniquet (Gen 7 and Older Generations) utilizing friction
  • Designed to allow more contact with the CAT when deploying
  • Injection Molded Nylon Case to stand up to rugged LE/MIL usage
  • Drainage Hole at the bottom of the case
  • Textured Front Panel
  • Medical Identifying PVC Cross Patch included
  • Multiple mounting positions to adjust the right height (can be mounted vertically, horizontally or inverted)
  • Available Mounting Options - Police Duty Belt (Blade-Tech TekLok Belt Attachment fits up to a 2.25" belt), MOLLE/PALS Attachment (Tactical Tailor Malice Clip), or a Raven Concealment Systems Paddle Attachment
  • Can be mounted to a Safariland Drop Leg Shroud in the accessory position (mounting hardware sold separately)
  • Can be mounted to Raven Concealment Systems ModuLoader System (not included)

Product name: Tru-Spec Men's Black Classic Pant
Description:
**Alterations Will Incur Additional Charges. We will contact you with the additionalcharge before the order is processed. **

WHEN YOU CAN'T DO CARGO . . . GO CLASSIC

There are times when cargo pockets just aren’t the right attire for the occasion. These pants are constructed with all the easy care features of the original 24-7 Series® pants but without the tactical style cargo pockets. Constructed from durable 6.5oz. 65/35 polyester cotton rip-stop with DWR water repellent coating and incorporating many low profile features that allows you to store your gear.;

Features

  1. TRU-SPEC® original PRYM snap with brass YKK® zipper
  2. Comfort fit slider waistband construction which eliminates the need for gathered elastic or adjustable side tabs and will accommodate either paddle style or inside-the-pants holsters
  3. 1½" belt loops with 2½" wide openings
  4. Extra deep front pockets
  5. 2-knife/accessory pockets
  6. Expandable back pockets with hook & loop closure
  7. 2-vertical zipper covered side seam pockets incorporated into the front pockets
  8. 2-special hidden zipper thigh pockets incorporated into the side seams

Introducing the new Model 730C – Superlite chain link handcuff with gray ceramic finish. Weighing in at just 5.2 ounces the Model 730 is near half the weight of a typical standard chain link handcuff. The Superlite is designed to meet the demands of law enforcement professionals while making the job a little easier. The smooth single-strand action has 21 locking positions with a push pin double lock.The Model 730C Superlite is National Institute of Justice Standard 0307.01 certified. Product name: Men's Danner 8" Lookout Side Zip
Description: To build the Lookout, we combined Danner’s legendary durability and support, with the unmatched comfort found in the all-new Danner Comfort System (DCS). This new duty offering delivers best-in-class durability, support, and cushioning right out of the box. It features a waterproof, polishable, full-grain leather and ripstop ballistic nylon upper that stands up to the job, and an all-new waterproof Danner Dry liner that pulls moisture away from the foot for all-season comfort. The cushioned comfort comes from a patent-pending, dual-density footbed, combining underfoot venting for maximum airflow and an Airthotic heel clip for support. A wider toe box allows for a more responsive fit, while the rugged outsole delivers outstanding traction and maneuverability.Pride of service comes in many forms. For us, it’s our dedication to creating a better product: to make it stronger, to make it lighter, to make it last. As we developed the Striker Torrent, we challenged ourselves to find the perfect balance between comfort and support, while ensuring that the new Striker would outlast its predecessor.

Product name: Men's Elbeco Navy ADU Ripstop Pant
Description: Durability and functionality are just a few words to describe Elbeco's ADU Ripstop Pant. Specifically designed for the Public Safety and EMT professional, the ADU Cargo and EMT pants have plenty of easily accessible storage with hook and loop closures keeping gear secure in its place. Additional features include our signature triple stitched crotch to prevent blow out, reinforced seat and knees to provide ultimate protection for longer wear and usage, and covert flex waistband providing an additional 2” stretch. The lightweight comfort and quick dry performance of RipStop with Nano Fluid Repellency technology keeps up with the demands of the industry with a polished, professional appearance.

Product name: ASP Side Breakaway Scabbard
Description:
Protection. Portation. Presentation. The three criteria of any baton scabbard. Each carrier must define a compromise between security and speed of presentation. It must provide a level of protection without compromising access. The case must secure the baton without hindering rapid deployment.

ASP Scabbards secure a baton during transport. They allow a firm grip and rapid presentation. Each design is fabricated for a specific purpose. Designs so unique that they are patented. Under the most severe tactical conditions, they have no equal.

The SideBreak Series is the foundation of the ASP gallery of baton scabbards. A retracted or expanded Friction Loc Baton may be rapidly presented, yet is securely retained during dynamic confrontations. Expanded batons may be presented out the side of the carrier. The SideBreak rotates to 7 distinct positions or may be locked upright on the belt. The Snap-Loc belt attachment can be adjusted to fit everything from a dress belt, duty belt and MOLLE gear.

The rotating SideBreak swivels to 12 distinct positions or may be locked in place on the duty belt.

Product name: Men's Rocky Alpha Force Zipper Waterproof Duty Boot
Description:
These hard-wearing Rocky® AlphaForce Waterproof Duty Black Boots are made with black full-grain leather and 1000-denier nylon fabric. Rocky AlphaForce boots are great EMT of occupational boots for tough work boot job needs. These lightweight, strong fabrics hold up even in the most extreme working conditions.

These duty boots have been built with Rocky Waterproof construction; this creates a barrier that is guaranteed to keep water out, so your feet will remain completely dry.

A side zipper makes it easy to get these boots on and off quickly.

Whether you're looking for durable black work boots, tactical boots, a great pair of waterproof boots or superior law enforcement boots... These Rocky AlphaForce boots are the right choice to help you get the job done!

Product name: Men's Rocky Alpha Force Zipper Waterproof Duty Boot
Description:
These hard-wearing Rocky® AlphaForce Waterproof Duty Black Boots are made with black full-grain leather and 1000-denier nylon fabric. Rocky AlphaForce boots are great EMT of occupational boots for tough work boot job needs. These lightweight, strong fabrics hold up even in the most extreme working conditions.

These duty boots have been built with Rocky Waterproof construction; this creates a barrier that is guaranteed to keep water out, so your feet will remain completely dry.

The Air-Port footbed is made from polyurethane and absorbs shock, but always reverts back to its earliest shape. The cushion footbed specifically targets your heel and metatarsal ridge, giving you support and comfort.

This boot features a non-metallic stabilizer, and has a non-marking RigiTrac outsole that provides oil and slip resistance.

A side zipper makes it easy to get these boots on and off quickly.

Whether you're looking for durable black work boots, tactical boots, a great pair of waterproof boots or superior law enforcement boots... These Rocky AlphaForce boots are the right choice to help you get the job done!

Product name: Blauer TacShell Winter Jacket
Description:
Sergeant = Minnetonka’snavy/gold chevrons both shoulders +2 PSSJ

Left shoulder = MinnetonkaPolice patch

Rightshoulder = Minnetonka Police patch

Leftchest = Badge patch - currently only have OFFICER rank on these

Rightchest = Minnetonka’s customer-owned navy border Flag +4 PSSJ above name

Right chest = 1stinitial last name emb 9mm silver 1811 NE-JKTsilver for all ranks

KEY FEATURES:

  • Waterproof, windproof, and breathable B.DRY® 3-layer Nylon rip-stop shell fabric with stretch
  • Drop shoulder design and articulated elbows for unrestricted movement
  • Multiple pocket configuration, including wearble electronics integration offer places for all your gear
  • Customizable pull down panels deploy from front and rear yokes
  • Hidden Napoleon pocket on left chest under storm flap for documents or gear

Outerwear for the 21st century law officer is here. Blauer surveyed professionals in several areas of law enforcement for their feedback. TacShell is the combined effort of Blauer design and your voice. Can you give us a better fit, a little longer but not too long so as to cover our gear? More nimble and quiet, waterproof enough to use as raingear but breathable enough to wear in spring and fall as a windbreaker? Don’t forget the hood, and the openings for weapon and radio, and make sure you put them in the right place. Plenty of pockets, also in the right places, and by the way, can you make it look like our current duty jacket so we don’t have to change them all out next year? That was for starters.

TacShell combines the features found in the best police outerwear and tactical jackets today. Our proprietary B.DRY waterproof, windproof breathable membrane keeps you warm, dry and comfortable, indoors or out. The stretch nylon outershell was developed to create a balance between long years of service life, quiet, and lightweight comfort. Even the ripstop pattern you see is engineered for a purpose, tenacity. The accent patch material, a smooth easy to clean dobby, gives the jacket more character interest.

TacShell pull-down panels are neatly hidden under front and rear yokes until you decide to deploy them for enhanced identification or visibility. A hidden Napoleon pocket on the left chest under the storm flap holds your documents or gear. The pull-down panels are easily customized with a variety of lettering and reflective options. There is a very portable waterproof hood that rolls neatly into the collar. Both sleeves have built in pockets for storage but also serve to access the shell for adding emblems and rank insignia. Multiple removable liner options from our System Outerwear line are available with TacShell.

Product name: Blauer Navy Soft Shell Jacket
Description:
Left Chest = Badge Patch

Right Chest = Embroidered First Initial/Last Name in Gold

Patches on both shoulders

KEY FEATURES:
  • Lightweight fleece-lined design provides superior warmth and wind resistance to most fleeces
  • Water resistant finish repels rain and snow
  • Zips in as a liner for Blauer System Outerwear Shell Jackets

This is the police jacket that you’ve been waiting for! For many years, most departments would not allow fleece jackets to be worn as an outer layer on duty due to their casual, less professional appearance. But ever since we first experienced this warm, comfortable outwear on the ski slopes in the 1990s, we have been determined to find a form that works for police officers and public safety works. The Blauer soft shell fleece jacket is the result of a decade of research and development, putting everything you love about fleece into an impressive and professional design approved by patrolmen, deputies and chiefs alike.

Our revolutionary design begins as a medium weight microfleece jacket that provides the perfect amount of warmth for cool days and nights. We then cover it in a softshell made from fade-resistant stretch nylon. Many companies use polyester for the shell, which is prone to picking and pilling over time. But our proprietary material is immune to this decomposition while still providing the freedom of movement you need. And we don’t stop there either – we use our proven water-repellent treatment to protect you from rain or snow and add elastic cuffs, microphone tabs and other features for ultimate functionality when the temperature drops.

We offer the softshell police fleece jacket in four colors, so you can get a black, green, dark navy or brown fleece jacket to fit the rest of your uniform. Once you’ve received your order, you can easily add your own emblems, badges and custom insignia to make it true department apparel. Product name: Blauer Navy Soft Shell Jacket
Description:
Left Chest = Badge Patch

Right Chest = Embroidered First Initial/Last Name in Gold

Patches on both shoulders w/ chevrons

KEY FEATURES:
  • Lightweight fleece-lined design provides superior warmth and wind resistance to most fleeces
  • Water resistant finish repels rain and snow
  • Zips in as a liner for Blauer System Outerwear Shell Jackets

This is the police jacket that you’ve been waiting for! For many years, most departments would not allow fleece jackets to be worn as an outer layer on duty due to their casual, less professional appearance. But ever since we first experienced this warm, comfortable outwear on the ski slopes in the 1990s, we have been determined to find a form that works for police officers and public safety works. The Blauer soft shell fleece jacket is the result of a decade of research and development, putting everything you love about fleece into an impressive and professional design approved by patrolmen, deputies and chiefs alike.

Our revolutionary design begins as a medium weight microfleece jacket that provides the perfect amount of warmth for cool days and nights. We then cover it in a softshell made from fade-resistant stretch nylon. Many companies use polyester for the shell, which is prone to picking and pilling over time. But our proprietary material is immune to this decomposition while still providing the freedom of movement you need. And we don’t stop there either – we use our proven water-repellent treatment to protect you from rain or snow and add elastic cuffs, microphone tabs and other features for ultimate functionality when the temperature drops.

We offer the softshell police fleece jacket in four colors, so you can get a black, green, dark navy or brown fleece jacket to fit the rest of your uniform. Once you’ve received your order, you can easily add your own emblems, badges and custom insignia to make it true department apparel. This jacket is part of the Blauer Systems Outerwear line, meaning you can wear it on its own or zip it into one of our outer shells as an inner liner. And did we mention that it’s machine washable? Check out more great features below and order your softshell police jacket today!

Product name: Blauer Armorskin Under Vest Shirt
Description:
Patches on both shoulders w/ CSO rockers

  • Durable uniform shirting fabric combined with breathable, moisture-wicking mesh fabric creates the ultimate performance uniform shirt that is both professional and comfortable
  • Designed to look like a Class A or B uniform shirt when worn under ArmorSkin®
  • LS Polyester Base Shirt matches Polyester Armorskin
  • Lightweight, moisture-wicking stretch mesh covers torso area for quick-dry comfort, body temperature regulation and advanced mobility
  • Durable 8.5 oz 100% Polyester fabric matches Blauer 100% Polyester shirting and pant fabric
  • Banded dress collar
  • 3-button center front placket
  • 2-button adjustable cuffs
  • Double pen pocket on left chest

Blauer's Revolutionary ArmorSkin® is the new way to wear concealed body armor. ArmorSkin® is the first ballistic vest cover system for law enforcement that provides relief from the heat and discomfort of conventional carriers, maintains a uniform look, and helps to alleviate lower back and hip pain. The system consists of the ArmorSkin® vest, which covers your existing carrier, an ArmorSkin® Base Shirt - our performance uniform shirt - worn as a base-layer or as an alternate uniform shirt, and an optional duty belt suspension system integrated into the vest.

Product name: Blauer Armorskin Under Vest Shirt - Short Sleeve
Description:
Patches on both shoulders w/ CSO rockers

Key Features:
  • Durable uniform shirting fabric combined with breathable, moisture-wicking mesh fabric creates the ultimate performance uniform shirt that is both professional and comfortable
  • Designed to look like a Class A or B uniform shirt when worn under ArmorSkin®
  • SS Polyester Base Shirt matches Polyester Armorskin
  • Lightweight, moisture-wicking stretch mesh covers torso area for quick-dry comfort, body temperature regulation and advanced mobility
  • Durable 8.5 oz 100% Polyester fabric matches Blauer 100% Polyester shirting and pant fabric
  • Convertible sport collar
  • 3-button center front placket
  • Double pen pocket on left chest

ArmorSkin® Base Shirt, the base layer of the ArmorSkin system is a hybrid shirt. A wicking fast dry knit shirt connected to a uniform shirt at the shoulders and sleeves. The wicking material extends under the arms of the shirt for added comfort and breathability. It is antimicrobial treated to inhibit the growth of odor producing bacteria.

The Base Shirt concept is similar to the military issued under vest shirts, which are so popular with the troops. While a conventional duty shirt or Supershirt can be worn under the vest, the ArmorSkin Base Shirt is a lot more comfortable and professional looking. In the station, without the vest on, the look is still professional and identification in the form of shoulder patches, is still visible.

The base knit fabric is specially engineered to prevent pilling and picking from abrasion of the outer vest for a neat appearance when the vest is not worn on top of it. Even so it is best to avoid contacting the knit directly with hook and loop straps from the soft body armor vest when possible. If cared for properly it should last as long or longer than regular uniform shirts.

Base Shirts are available in all of the popular uniform fabrics and color from which we make our uniform shirts; polyester pictured here, wool blends, rayon blends and cotton ripstop blends in some colors also are available. Blauer’s quality uniform shirt fabrics guarantees base shirts will look good for a long time.

Throw on the loaded ArmorSkin® vest carrier cover and you are in uniform.

Product name: Tru-Spec Men's Olive Drab Poly/Cotton Ripstop Cargo Pants
Description:
WORK HARD, FEEL COMFORTABLE & LOOK GREAT

The best fitting, most comfortable tactical pants on the market. The original 24-7 Series®Tactical Pant, designed with an engineered dimensional fit that is just right for on-duty or off-duty wear. With features like a comfortable slider waistband, deep cargo pockets that are designed to accommodate a concealed weapon and reinforced knees that are designed with special pockets for inserting pads, the pants cannot be beat for utility or comfort. 6.5oz. 65/35 Polyester Cotton Rip-Stop fabrics are DWR water repellent coated. These are the pants that started it all.;

Features

  1. TRU-SPEC® original PRYM snap with brass YKK® zipper
  2. Comfort fit slider waistband
  3. 2" wide belt loops
  4. Extra deep front pockets
  5. 2-knife/accessory pockets
  6. Expandable back pockets with hook & loop closure
  7. Two cargo pockets with hook & loop closure and bellowed side gussets that contain 2-internal magazine compartments
  8. Cell phone/magazine pocket on outside of cargo pockets
  9. Double reinforced knee with built in knee pad pockets

Product name: Men's Reebok Sublite Shoe
Description:
Reebok Sublite Cushion Tactical

The Reebok Sublite Cushion Tactical shoe achieves maximum lightness and flexibility in a tactical shoe, making it one piece of equipment that won’t weigh you down. With deep flex grooves, the SubLite foam midsole reduces weight and allows for greater range of motion. Rubber pads provide traction at heel strike and forefoot takeoff while minimizing weight. Mesh uppers allow for ultimate breathability and moisture transfer for all day cooling comfort. A removable and washable MemoryTech Massage footbed adapts to the unique contours of your foot with profiled bumps that soothe tight muscles with every step for a treat your feet will thank you for. These shoes are ASTM F2892 compliant, EH rated, free of metal and have a slip resistant outsole to provide additional protection.

Features of Reebok Sublite Cushion Tactical

  • Full foot flex grooves for improved mobility and flex with every step
  • Removable and washable MemoryTech Massage footbed
  • SubLite foam midsole for lightweight cushioning and soft support
  • ASTM F2892 compliant
  • Soft toe
  • EH rated protection

Product name: Rocky AlphaForce Composite Toe
Description:
One of the key features of the Rocky AlphaForce Composite Toe Waterproof Duty Boot is its non-metallic composite toe cap. It meets ASTM standards for impact and compression. These boots also meet electrical hazard resistance requirements.

An additional feature of these duty boots is Rocky Waterproof construction. It combines a waterproof inner layer with the upper, providing a barrier that keeps water out and feet dry.

A key comfort feature of this style is its contoured removable Air-Port Cushion Footbed, providing direct underfoot cushion comfort. The polyurethane material always returns to its original shape. Some open celled foams feel comfortable to the initial touch, but break down faster than a product made with polyurethane. Plus, this footbed is extra-thick in the heel contact area to give you additional comfort.

The Rigitrac molded EVA/rubber outsole is oil- and slip-resistant. It offers great traction and is non-marking.

Product name: Ergodyne Proflex Thermal Utility Glove
Description:
When cold weather tries to freeze dry your on-the-job resolve, tell it to say hello to my little friends - The Thermal Series. Offering maximum firepower when it comes to wind and waterproof production, plus full dexterity and comfort. During winter months (most of the year where we come from) work gloves must do four basic things to get hands comfortably through the winter: keep 'em warm, dry, able to securely grip winter's icy surfaces, and protected against daily workplace bumping and bruising. The ProFlex Thermal Series combines patented technology to deliver on all four.

  • Insulated-40 grams of 3M Thinsulate insulation
  • Durable- reinforced synthetic leather palm for a secure grip in cold temperatures
  • Lightweight Protection-made with a breathable padded spandex material and foam knuckle pad

Product name: Ergodyne Proflex Thermal Waterproof Utility Glove
Description:
When cold weather tries to freeze dry your on-the-job resolve, tell it to say hello to my little friends - The Thermal Series. Offering maximum firepower when it comes to wind and waterproof production, plus full dexterity and comfort. During winter months (most of the year where we come from) work gloves must do four basic things to get hands comfortably through the winter: keep 'em warm, dry, able to securely grip winter's icy surfaces, and protected against daily workplace bumping and bruising. The ProFlex Thermal Series combines patented technology to deliver on all four.

  • Insulated-40 grams of 3M Thinsulate insulation
  • Waterproof liner
  • Durable- reinforced synthetic leather palm for a secure grip in cold temperatures
  • Lightweight Protection-made with a breathable padded spandex material and foam knuckle pad
  • Comfortable Fit- hook & loop closure keeps snow and cold air out and gloves secure on the toughest jobs
  • Terry Thumb Brow Wipe- soft, comfortable place to wipe sweat from your brow

Description: To build the Lookout, we combined Danner’s legendary durability and support, with the unmatched comfort found in the all-new Danner Comfort System (DCS). This new duty offering delivers best-in-class durability, support, and cushioning right out of the box. It features a waterproof, polishable, full-grain leather and ripstop ballistic nylon upper that stands up to the job, and an all-new waterproof Danner Dry liner that pulls moisture away from the foot for all-season comfort. The cushioned comfort comes from a patent-pending, dual-density footbed, combining underfoot venting for maximum airflow and an Airthotic heel clip for support. A wider toe box allows for a more responsive fit, while the rugged outsole delivers outstanding traction and maneuverability.Pride of service comes in many forms. For us, it’s our dedication to creating a better product: to make it stronger, to make it lighter, to make it last. As we developed the Striker Torrent, we challenged ourselves to find the perfect balance between comfort and support, while ensuring that the new Striker would outlast its predecessor.

Description:
When cold weather tries to freeze dry your on-the-job resolve, tell it to say hello to my little friends - The Thermal Series. Offering maximum firepower when it comes to wind and waterproof production, plus full dexterity and comfort. During winter months (most of the year where we come from) work gloves must do four basic things to get hands comfortably through the winter: keep 'em warm, dry, able to securely grip winter's icy surfaces, and protected against daily workplace bumping and bruising. The ProFlex Thermal Series combines patented technology to deliver on all four.

  • Insulated-40 grams of 3M Thinsulate insulation
  • Waterproof Liner
  • Durable- reinforced synthetic leather palm for a secure grip in cold temperatures
  • Lightweight Protection-made with a breathable padded spandex material and foam knuckle pad
  • Comfortable Fit- hook & loop closure keeps snow and cold air out and gloves secure on the toughest jobs
  • Terry Thumb Brow Wipe- soft, comfortable place to wipe sweat from your brow

The Leatherman Raptor shears features the necessary tools for uniformed medical professionals to safely and quickly go to work in an emergency situation. Developed with the input of special operations medics, EMTs and fire professionals familiar with standard medical shears, the Raptor shears were crafted with just the right balance of multipurpose features for medical-specific ops without an overkill of tools to complicate sometimes life-threatening situations. Product name: Elbeco Men's Poly/Wool Navy Plain Pant
Description:

Product name: Tru-Spec Men's Khaki HIdden Zipper Pant
Description:
WHEN YOU CAN'T DO CARGO . . . GO CLASSIC

There are times when cargo pockets just aren’t the right attire for the occasion. These pants are constructed with all the easy care features of the original 24-7 Series® pants but without the tactical style cargo pockets. Constructed from durable 6.5oz. 65/35 polyester cotton rip-stop with DWR water repellent coating and incorporating many low profile features that allows you to store your gear.;

  5. Two knife/accessory pockets
  6. Expandable back pockets with hook & loop closure
  7. Two vertical zipper covered side seam pockets incorporated into the front pockets
  8. Two special hidden zipper thigh pockets incorporated into the side seams

Product name: Littman Master Cardiology 22" Stethoscope
Description:
Details

  • Outstanding acoustics: The highest in Littmann mechanical stethoscopes.
  • Tunable diaphragm: Hear high or low frequency sounds by slightly adjusting pressure on the chestpiece.
  • Dual-lumen tubing: Two sound paths in one tube eliminates the rubbing noise of traditional double tubes.
  • Headset is easily adjusted for individual fit and comfort. Angled eartubes align with ear canals.
  • Includes Special Procedures Adaptor for pediatric or neonatal auscultation.

The 3M™ Littmann® Master Cardiology™ Stethoscope is characterized by the best acoustic response in the Littmann mechanical stethoscope line; with a tunable diaphragm, dual-lumen tubing, and a precision, ergonomically designed, stainless steel chestpiece.

The 3M™ Littmann® Master Cardiology™ Stethoscope features tunable diaphragm technology—a 3M invention—that lets clinicians hear different frequency sounds by simply adjusting the pressure on the chestpiece. Unlike two-sided models, there’s no need to turn over and reposition the chestpiece. Hold the chestpiece with light pressure to hear low frequency sounds; press a little more to hear higher frequency sounds. This time-saving feature allows the healthcare provider to focus on the patient, while the non-chill rim provides patient comfort.

Headset tension is easily adjusted for head size and comfort by squeezing together or pulling apart the eartubes. Snap-tight, soft-sealing eartips conform to individual ears for an excellent acoustic seal and comfortable fit. Eartips snap firmly onto the ends of the eartubes and, for safety, require a significant effort to remove.

Resilient next-generation tubing retains its shape and flexibility even after folding tightly into a pocket. It provides longer stethoscope life due to improved resistance to skin oils and alcohol, and is less likely to pick up stains. Next-generation tubing is not made with natural rubber latex, a benefit to sensitive medical professionals and their patients. And, to play its part in the protection of human health and the environment, the next-generation tubing does not contain phthalate plasticizers.

The Master Cardiology stethoscope is made in the USA for consistent quality. It comes complete with large and small soft-sealing eartips, large firm eartips, Special Procedures Adapter, and instructions.

Product name: Boston Leather 5" Leather Radio Holder with Swivel
Description:
5" Tall Deluxe Universal Radio Holder with Swivel Attachment

The Deluxe Universal Radio Holder features a wide adjustable leather lined VELCRO® strap. The holders are vailable in two sizes to accommodate just about every radio. A locking flap reduces the possibility of unwanted release. The holder has a leather covered steel backwall. This is formed to provide an uncompromising base for the radio to rest on. The holder easily mounts on a belt with two safety "pull the dots" snaps. Nickel snaps.

Product name: Safariland Open Top Magazine/Cuff Holder
Description: The Model 573 is a handy combination magazine and handcuff pouch, complete with a quick on/off paddle. It featues suede lining and holds the items securely and quietly. It features an Allen screw to adjust tension for magazine size. The unique paddle design is rigid in the center and flexible around the edges and includes a self-locking belt hook. Fits up to 1.75 in. (45 mm) belt.

Product name: Bianchi Accumold Outer Duty Belt
Description: The Model 7950 Duty Belt features 4-part laminate construction for firmness and holster support. It features a Duraskin™ exterior with loop lining for use with the Bianchi® 7205 Liner Belt. 2.25 in. (58 mm) belt width. It features the Tri-Release™ shatter-resistant polymer buckle. Its 3-point release provides extra security from inadvertent release. Complements AccuMold® Elite™ accessories.

Product name: Model 6360 ALS®/SLS Mid-Ride, Level III Retention™ Duty Holster w/ Light
Description:
The 6360 ALS®/SLS Mid-ride duty holster is sturdy, lightweight, and provides an extra measure of security while on patrol. The ALS® (Automatic Locking System) builds on the foundation of the SLS (Self Locking System) to offer Level III Retention™. In addition to the SLS, Safariland's patented ALS locks the firearm into place immediately upon holstering, while the rotating hood and tension device ensure added security. The 6360 holster can be easily upgraded to Level IV Retention® using the optional Sentry attachment.

The 6360 ALS®/SLS Mid-ride is constructed of durable SafariLaminate™ and is lined with suede to protect the gun’s sights and finish. For a snug and comfortable fit, the mid-ride belt loop allows the holster to ride close to the body.

Product name: NAR COMBAT TQ CASE G7 RIGID BLACK BASKETWEAVE
Description:
Always have the Gen 7 C-A-T® within easy reach, yet keep it protected in a rigid holder capable of withstanding foot pursuits, combative subjects and daily patrol functions without allowing it to fall out of the carrier, The Gen 7 C-A-T® RIGID TQ Case® was designed to provide personnel with the capability to carry the life-saving C-A-T® Tourniquet on their person by easily mounting it to their duty/patrol/pistol belt, where it is needed most. It can be mounted either vertically or horizontally and can also be attached to a Safariland® Drop Leg Shroud using the existing holes (the case mounts with 2 screws in the middle of the case). The Injection Molded Nylon Case provides strength and durability as it holds the Gen 7 C-A-T® Tourniquet tightly in place with no straps or covers. The tourniquet can be quickly and easily removed by grabbing and pulling the top part of the C-A-T® Tourniquet. The case also includes a hook and loop cross to identify it as medical equipment.

  • Allows you to carry a Gen 7 C-A-T® Tourniquet on your duty/patrol/pistol belt so you have life-saving equipment on your person at all times
  • Blade-Tech TekLok Belt Attachment fits up to a 2.25 in. belt
  • Can be mounted either vertically or horizontally or attached to a Safariland Drop Leg Shroud
  • Injection Molded Nylon Case to stand up to rugged LE/MIL usage
  • Cross medical identifier patch included
  • 4.75”H x 2.25”W x 2”D; weighs 3.8 oz
  • Compatible with the C-A-T® Gen 7 (sold separately).

Product name: Streamlight TLR-1 Rail Mounted Light
Description:
Intensely bright, virtually indestructible rail-mounted tactical light which attaches to almost any gun in seconds.

  • Powered by two 3-volt CR123 lithium batteries with 10-year storage life
  • 300 lumens; 2.5 hours regulated run time; 12,000 candela peak beam intensity
  • Solid-state current regulation for consistent illumination level.
  • Rail grip clamp system securely attaches/detaches quickly and safely with no tools and without putting your hands in front of muzzle
  • Mounts directly to handguns with Glock-style rails and to all MIL-STD-1913 (Picatinny) rails.
  • Includes keys for Glock-style, Picatinny, Beretta 90two, S&W 99 and S&W TSW
  • Machined aluminum sealed construction with black anodized finsih
  • Ambidextrous momentary/steady on/off switch
  • Highly accurate sight repeatability when remounting
  • Fits existing light bearing holsters
  • 4.18 oz.
  • Lithium Battery Notice under Documentation
  • IPX7 rated design; waterproof to 1 meter for 30 minutes.
  • Remote switches are available as optional accessories and must be used in conjunction with 69130 remote door switch. All switches and door switch are sold separately. Reference TLR Accessories Brochure in DOCS/INFO tab for more information.
  • Assembled in USA

Product name: Survival Armor Paladin Level 2 Ballistic Vest

Top-of-the-Line ballistic armor package. Extremely light weight, wearable, along with exceptional ballistic performance, makes the Paladin the top choice for comfort and ballistic performance.

Product name: 5.11 Tactical Stryke Pant - Coyote
Description:
The 5.11 Stryke® Pant is what all other pants want to be. Made of our patent-pending two-way Flex-Tac® mechanical stretch fabric, finished with stain- and soil-resistant Teflon®, the 5.11 Stryke® pant is exceptionally durable. With 12 pockets, reinforcements in strategic places, and a self-adjusting waistband, it’s high-performance functionality at its finest.

  • Two-way Flex-Tac® mechanical stretch
  • Front pockets sized for EDC items
  • 12 pockets
  • 6.76 oz. Flex- Tac® ripstop fabric
  • Self- adjusting tunnel waistband
  • Gusseted construction
  • Articulated knees (Internal knee pad ready)

Product name: ASP Hinged Handcuff
Description:
ASP’s revolutionary, forged aluminum frame restraints—a new standard in strength, speed, precision and safety, all in an incredibly lightweight handcuff.


ASP’s exclusive Ultra Cuffs represent the most significant advances in restraint design in more than a century. These handcuffs were designed, tested, revised, re-tested and perfected in the field, with input from officers and tactical instructors around the world. The result is a restraint system with materials, construction and a feature set that simply can’t be found in any other handcuffs:

  • Forged aluminum frame: Forged from 7075 T6 ordnance-grade aluminum, Ultra Cuff frames are rigid and incredibly strong, yet lightweight. Forging—as opposed to the stamped steel parts found in other restraints—also eliminates rough or sharp edges; the smooth, rounded Ultra Cuff frame is more ergonomic, and safer for both officer and subject.
  • Conical, flat contact bow: The geometry of the bow fits a wider range of wrists, and a flat contact area improves application speed and accuracy. Bows are also highly radiused, to prevent injury. Ultra Cuffs are available with either steel bows or aluminum bows, to lighten the load even more.
  • Dual-sided, single-turn keyways: Ultra Cuffs feature keyways and double lock slots on both sides of each frame, and both the primary lock and double lock are released by turning the key in a single direction. Double lock slots feature colored indicators that provide instant recognition of lock status. All of these features add up to making cuff application, adjustment, double-locking and removal faster and easier.
  • Replaceable Lock Sets: The lock assemblies are unitized and replaceable. This allows them to be field-serviced when needed, and provides the unique option to change Lock Sets to suit different agency preferences, or to switch to a high-security configuration.* The construction of the Lock Sets, and their placement within the forged frame, also makes them highly-resistant to shimming.

Hinge Ultra Cuffs feature a stainless steel, four-point rotation hinges. Ultra Cuffs are also available in Chain or Rigid models.

We recommend adding our specially-formulated Glide Baton and Cuff Lubricant to your order, to keep your gear in peak operating condition.

*IMPORTANT: 2 Pawl High Security cuffs require a special key, and will not open with a standard handcuff key.

  • 65% polyester / 35% cotton
  • H2Tech™ liquid repellant
  • H2Ultradye™ color retention
  • Snugtex adjustable waistband
  • Double stitched for toughness
  • Double fabric seat for durability
  • Double clasp closure
  • Velcro® closures on all cargo pockets
  • Bartacks at all stress points for extra durability

Product name: Reebok 6" Sublite Cushion Tactical Side Zip Boot
Description:
Enjoy ultimate comfort, flexibility and responsiveness with the Reebok 8" Sublite Cushion Tactical Side Zip Boot. Built with a YKK® zipper for easy on and off. Reebok’s MemoryTech Massage footbed adapts to the contours of your foot to provide immediate cushioning. Full-foot flex grooves deliver improved mobility and flex with every step while the Sublite foam midsole provides lightweight cushioning and soft support. The durable leather and ballistic nylon uppers include a moisture-wicking nylon mesh lining for enhanced comfort.

PRODUCT SPECS
  • Leather and ballistic nylon upper
  • YKK® side zipper for fast on and off
  • MemoryTech Massage footbed adapts to the contours of your foot to provide immediate cushioning
  • Sublite foam midsole provides lightweight cushioning and soft support
  • Targeted rubber on the outsole for traction and durability
  • Full-foot flex grooves for improved mobility and flex with every step
  • Moisture wicking nylon mesh lining
  • Extremely lightweight and flexible

Product name: Danner Lookout Side Zip 8" Waterproof
Description:
The Danner Lookout 8 Inch Waterproof Side Zip Tactical Boot 23824 is made from a durable and long wearing full grain leather and nylon upper construction. This boot comes with a side zipper to allow you to get in and out of your boots quickly while the 8 inch height supplies a stable and supportive construction. The boot keeps its shape from a lightweight nylon shank. This boot is a great choice for those looking for a lightweight tactical boot.

Specifics
  • All-new Danner Comfort System (DCS) delivers best-in-class durability, support and comfort
  • Durable, waterproof, polishable, full-grain leather and ripstop ballistic nylon upper
  • Waterproof Danner Dry liner pulls moisture away from the foot for greater comfort
  • Semi-locking side-zip provides a fast and secure fit
  • Anatomical design and broader toe box for responsive fit
  • Patent-pending plush dual-density footbed for cushioning, underfoot venting for maximum airflow and Airthotic heel clip for support
  • Danner Lookout slip-resistant outsole with dynamic lug pattern for superior traction and maneuverability
  • Nylon shank
  • 8" height
  • 54 oz.
  • Imported

Product name: Tactical Mic Clip
Description:
• PROFESSIONAL The Tactical Mic Klip is a potentially life-saving innovation for those who use radio communication. It creates a much more secure and sensible hold than simply clipping the radio to your shirt. Its purpose is to make your gear more reliable so you can perform duties as intended without interruptions such as readjusting to replacing a loose radio microphone.
  • SECURE- When the TMK is installed, it doesn’t come off accidentally. The slide-on mechanism doesn’t slide off, even in a struggle or at full sprint. The angle of the button mount is designed to be easy to apply and remove intentionally, while doing away with accidental mishaps. No more grabbing your radio to keep it in place or worrying you won’t be able to call in your position quickly. Easy to use, near impossible to fail.
  • VERSATILE- TMK provides a sense of security for your mic and the added safety that comes with it, to all radio users in public or private sectors. You can install it with any button on your uniform, most commonly mounted on the front or shoulder. It improves the function of an earpiece as well- the radio doesn’t bounce around as much or tug the earpiece away from the ear when using TMK. After all, you’re never quite sure when you’ll need to spring into action.
  • TRUSTED - LEO all over the country are fast adopting this innovative product. It’s simple to implement, inexpensive, and vast improves the function of your radio microphone. Once you try TMK, you’ll wonder how you ever got along without it.

Product name: Blauer Armorskin Navy Vest Carrier
Description:
Key Features:
  • Designed to look like a uniform shirt when worn over an ArmorSkin® Base Shirt, ArmorSkin® helps to maintain a professional appearance and your tactical advantage in the field
  • Polyester ArmorSkin matches: LS Polyester ArmorSkin Base Shirt, SS Polyester ArmorSkin Base Shirt, and Polyester ArmorSkin Winter Base Shirt
  • Universal armor fit and easy adjustment at shoulders and sides allows your existing ballistic armor and carrier to be fitted and worn exactly as it would under a uniform shirt and according to the manufacturer's instructions
  • Mesh lining and side panels are lightweight and provide more breathability and quick-dry comfort
  • Side openings with stretch nylon mesh and heavy duty one-way YKK zippers offer advanced mobility, quick donning and doffing, and more coverage
  • Durable 8.5 oz 100% Polyester fabric matches Blauer 100% Polyester shirting and pant fabric
  • Pleated patch pockets with scalloped flaps, pencil slots and hook and loop closure
  • Epaulets
  • Center mic tab
  • Traditional 5-crease militarty style (stiched)
  • Optional tie bar included

Blauer's revolutionary ArmorSkin is the way to wear concealed body armor. ArmorSkin is the first body armor integration uniform system for law enforcement that provides relief from the heat and discomfort of conventional body armor carriers, maintains a police uniform look, and helps to alleviate lower back and hip pain.

The system consists of the ArmorSkin vest, which covers your existing body armor carrier, a Blauer Base Shirt – our performance uniform shirt- worn as a base layer or as an alternate uniform shirt, and an optional duty belt suspension system integrated into the vest. In the office the outer layer, ArmorSkin carrier and concealed soft body armor, can be removed for relief from the heat and weight of the vest.

When worn over a Base Shirt, ArmorSkin allows you to maintain a normal professional appearance, maintaining your tactical advantage in the field. With easy adjustment at the shoulders and sides and universal armor fit, your existing ballistic police body armor and pads can be fitted and worn exactly as it would under a uniform shirt. Mesh lining and side panels are lightweight, breathable and dry quickly, maximizing comfort.

With side openings utilizing stretch nylon mesh and two-way zippers, a greater range of motion is achieved making it easier to don and doff the body armor carrier. Quick adjustments to the fit of the concealed armor are also possible during your shift. Just like the Blauer SuperShirt, ArmorSkin also features epaulets, pleated patch pockets with scalloped flaps, Napoleon pockets, a pencil slot, center mic tab, and traditional 5-crease military style stitched in. ArmorSkin is available in polyester shown above, as well as wool, rayon and cotton ripstop blends.

Until now external carriers had to be matched with the concealed soft body armor manufacturers outer carrier in order to be covered by the original manufacturers warranty. ArmorSkin uses the concealed armor carrier and all 4 (or 6) hook and loop connector straps and fits virtually every brand of armor made. There is no effect on performance of the ballistics or the fit of the soft body armor since it is worn as if it were concealed under a uniform shirt.

Product name: Men's Reebok Sublite Shoe [CLONE]
Description:
Reebok Sublite Cushion Tactical

The Reebok Sublite Cushion Tactical shoe achieves maximum lightness and flexibility in a tactical shoe, making it one piece of equipment that won’t weigh you down. With deep flex grooves, the SubLite foam midsole reduces weight and allows for greater range of motion. Rubber pads provide traction at heel strike and forefoot takeoff while minimizing weight. Mesh uppers allow for ultimate breathability and moisture transfer for all day cooling comfort. A removable and washable MemoryTech Massage footbed adapts to the unique contours of your foot with profiled bumps that soothe tight muscles with every step for a treat your feet will thank you for. These shoes are ASTM F2892 compliant, EH rated, free of metal and have a slip resistant outsole to provide additional protection.

Features of Reebok Sublite Cushion Tactical

  • Full foot flex grooves for improved mobility and flex with every step
  • Removable and washable MemoryTech Massage footbed
  • SubLite foam midsole for lightweight cushioning and soft support
  • ASTM F2892 compliant
  • Soft toe
  • EH rated protection
  • Metal free
  • Slip resistant outsole
  • Mid height design

    7. Inset cargo pockets for a streamline appearance
    8. Easy access DropN pocket behind each cargo pocket that accommodates most cell phones

A sleek pen light that conveniently fits in your pocket. Ideal for anyone that needs a compact, durable light to carry on a daily basis. Now shining brighter at 90 lumens!

  • White C4® LED delivers 90 lumens; 860 candela; 58m beam; runs 6.5 hours
  • Push button tail switch momentary or constant on operation
  • Includes two "AAA" alkaline batteries and tear-resistant nylon holster
  • Type II MIL-SPEC abrasion and corrosion-resistant anodized aircraft aluminum construction with unbreakable, scratch-resistant polycarbonate lens
  • IPX4 water-resistant; 1m impact resistance tested
  • About the size of a marker, it conveniently fits in your pocket and a removable pocket clip ensures it stays in place

These hard-wearing Rocky® AlphaForce Waterproof Duty Black Boots are made with black full-grain leather and 1000-denier nylon fabric. Rocky AlphaForce boots are great EMT of occupational boots for tough work boot job needs. These lightweight, strong fabrics hold up even in the most extreme working conditions.

A side zipper makes it easy to get these boots on and off quickly.

Whether you're looking for durable black work boots, tactical boots, a great pair of waterproof boots or superior law enforcement boots... These Rocky AlphaForce boots are the right choice to help you get the job done!

Product name: Tru-Spec Men's Cargo Pocket Pant
Description:
**Alterations Will Incur Additional Charges. We will contact you with the additionalcharge before the order is processed. **

WORK HARD, FEEL COMFORTABLE & LOOK GREAT

The best fitting, most comfortable tactical pants on the market. The original 24-7 Series®Tactical Pant, designed with an engineered dimensional fit that is just right for on-duty or off-duty wear. With features like a comfortable slider waistband, deep cargo pockets that are designed to accommodate a concealed weapon and reinforced knees that are designed with special pockets for inserting pads, the pants cannot be beat for utility or comfort. 6.5oz. 65/35 polyester cotton rip-stop fabrics are DWR water repellent coated. These are the pants that started it all.;

Features

  1. TRU-SPEC® original PRYM snap with brass YKK® zipper
  2. Comfort fit slider waistband
  3. 2" wide belt loops
  4. Extra deep front pockets
  5. Two knife/accessory pockets
  6. Expandable back pockets with hook & loop closure
  7. Two cargo pockets with hook & loop closure and bellowed side gussets that contain 2-internal magazine compartments
  8. Utility pocket on outside of cargo pockets
  9. Double reinforced knee with built in knee pad pockets

Description:
**Alterations Will Incur Additional Charges. We will contact you with the additionalcharge before the order is processed. **

The best fitting, most comfortable tactical pants on the market. The original 24-7 Series®Tactical Pant, designed with an engineered dimensional fit that is just right for on-duty or off-duty wear. With features like a comfortable slider waistband, deep cargo pockets that are designed to accommodate a concealed weapon and reinforced knees that are designed with special pockets for inserting pads, the pants cannot be beat for utility or comfort. 6.5oz. 65/35 Polyester Cotton Rip-Stop fabrics are DWR water repellent coated.   4. Extra deep front pockets
  5. 2-knife/accessory pockets
  6. Expandable back pockets with hook & loop closure
  7. 2-cargo pockets with hook & loop closure and bellowed side gussets that contain 2-internal magazine compartments
  8. Cell phone/magazine pocket on outside of cargo pockets
  9. Double reinforced knee with built in knee pad pockets

  • 12 total pockets, including double- deep cargo pockets
  • Rinse washed
  • YKK® zippers and Prym® snaps

Product name: Blauer 100% Poly Med Blue Men's Undervest Shirt Short Sleeve
Description:
Left shoulder = Inver Grove Heights PDpatch with reserve rocker

Rightshoulder = Inver Grove Heights PD patch with reserve rocker +2 PSS
Key Features:
  • Durable uniform shirting fabric combined with breathable, moisture-wicking mesh fabric creates the ultimate performance uniform shirt that is both professional and comfortable
  • Designed to look like a Class A or B uniform shirt when worn under ArmorSkin®
  • SS Polyester Base Shirt matches Polyester Armorskin
  • Lightweight, moisture-wicking stretch mesh covers torso area for quick-dry comfort, body temperature regulation and advanced mobility
  • Durable 8.5 oz 100% Polyester fabric matches Blauer 100% Polyester shirting and pant fabric
  • Convertible sport collar
  • 3-button center front placket
  • Double pen pocket on left chest

ArmorSkin® Base Shirt, the base layer of the ArmorSkin system is a hybrid shirt. A wicking fast dry knit shirt connected to a uniform shirt at the shoulders and sleeves. The wicking material extends under the arms of the shirt for added comfort and breathability. It is antimicrobial treated to inhibit the growth of odor producing bacteria.

The Base Shirt concept is similar to the military issued under vest shirts, which are so popular with the troops. While a conventional duty shirt or Supershirt can be worn under the vest, the ArmorSkin Base Shirt is a lot more comfortable and professional looking. In the station, without the vest on, the look is still professional and identification in the form of shoulder patches, is still visible.

The base knit fabric is specially engineered to prevent pilling and picking from abrasion of the outer vest for a neat appearance when the vest is not worn on top of it. Even so it is best to avoid contacting the knit directly with hook and loop straps from the soft body armor vest when possible. If cared for properly it should last as long or longer than regular uniform shirts.

Base Shirts are available in all of the popular uniform fabrics and color from which we make our uniform shirts; polyester pictured here, wools, rayons and cotton ripstop blends in some colors also are available. Blauer's quality uniform shirt fabrics guarantees base shirts will look good for a long time.

Throw on the loaded ArmorSkin® vest carrier cover and you are in uniform.

Product name: Ergodyne Proflex Thermal Utility Glove - Lined
Description:
When cold weather tries to freeze dry your on-the-job resolve, tell it to say hello to my little friends - The Thermal Series. Offering maximum firepower when it comes to wind and waterproof production, plus full dexterity and comfort. During winter months (most of the year where we come from) work gloves must do four basic things to get hands comfortably through the winter: keep 'em warm, dry, able to securely grip winter's icy surfaces, and protected against daily workplace bumping and bruising. The ProFlex Thermal Series combines patented technology to deliver on all four.

  • Insulated-40 grams of 3M Thinsulate insulation
  • Durable- reinforced synthetic leather palm for a secure grip in cold temperatures
  • Lightweight Protection-made with a breathable padded spandex material and foam knuckle pad
  • Comfortable Fit- hook & loop closure keeps snow and cold air out and gloves secure on the toughest jobs
  • Terry Thumb Brow Wipe- soft, comfortable place to wipe sweat from your brow

Product name: Streamlight Stinger Battery
Description:
Streamlight has created a battery stick that specifically fits their line of popular and powerful Stinger/PolyStinger flashlights. This battery stick's chemistry is Ni-MH, that is, nickel-metal-hydride, and it's meant to be a replacement for other Ni-MH batteries. Streamlight is a well-respected American company that manufactures the toughest and most capable flashlights out there. A battery stick is similar to a battery pack, in that it is actually multiple batteries bundled together. The voltage on this battery stick is 3.6V, more than double the voltage of a typical alkaline primary cell. This battery stick is Sub-C in terms of size. The Streamlight battery stick is certainly going to become an essential part of your Streamlight supplies!

Features:
  • Specifically fits Streamlight's line of popular and powerful Stinger/PolyStinger flashlights
  • Chemistry is Ni-MH (nickel-metal-hydride)
  • Is a replacement for other Ni-MH batteries
  • Voltage is 3.6V
  • Size is Sub-C
  • Encompasses up to 1,000 charge-recharge cycles
Specifications:
  • Chemistry: Ni-MH
  • Size: Sub-C
  • Voltage: 3.6V
  • Charge-recharge cycles: 1,000
  • Dimensions:
    • Length: 5.125 in.

Additional features on the Tactical Fleece include microphone clips at each shoulder, zippered handwarmer pockets, twin internal pockets, and a tapered fit for a professional profile.

Product name: TruSpec Black GEN-III ICWCS Level-1 Bottom
Description:
MULTIPLE LAYERS OF WARMTH

The Extreme Cold Weather Clothing System, or Gen-III ECWCS is a protective cold weather clothing system created originally by the United States Army Natick Soldier Research, Development and Engineering Center. This system consisted of a parka and trousers plus 20 other individual clothing, headwear and footwear items which are used in various combinations to meet the cold weather environmental requirements of the US military. Our baselayer level garments are based off these designs to give our garments the same quality and utility as the base layers of this system. The Level-1 garments draw moisture away from the skin to the outer layers of clothing providing great warmth without weight, is quick drying and compresses to reduce volume when packed.;


  1. Elastic waistband
  2. Access fly
  3. Flat locked construction
  4. Microban® anti-microbial properties in the fabric to aid in odor defense
  5. Double needle stitched leg openings

Description:
EXTRA SOFT, EXTRA WARM

Extra warmth when it’s extra cold. Fleece has many of wool's qualities but weighs a fraction of the lightest available wool fabrics. Used in some of the high-performance outdoor clothing, microfleece is a lightweight, warm and soft fabric that is hydrophobic, holding less than 1% of its weight in water retaining much of its insulating powers even when wet. Product name: Safariland Glock 17 Gen4 No Light Right Draw Holster
Description:
Safariland Glock 17 Gen4 No Light Right Draw Holster

Model 6360 ALS®/SLS Mid-Ride, Level III Retention™ Duty Holster

Safariland Glock 17 Gen4 No Light Right Draw Holster

The 6360 ALS®/SLS Mid-ride duty holster is sturdy, lightweight, and provides an extra measure of security while on patrol. The ALS® (Automatic Locking System) builds on the foundation of the SLS (Self Locking System) to offer Level III Retention™. In addition to the SLS, Safariland's patented ALS locks the firearm into place immediately upon holstering, while the rotating hood and tension device ensure added security. The 6360 holster can be easily upgraded to Level IV Retention® using the optional Sentry attachment.

The 6360 ALS®/SLS Mid-ride is constructed of durable SafariLaminate™ and is lined with suede to protect the gun’s sights and finish. For a snug and comfortable fit, the mid-ride belt loop allows the holster to ride close to the body.

Description:
Safariland Glock 17 Gen4 With TLR-1 Light Right Draw Holster

Model 6360 ALS®/SLS Mid-Ride, Level III Retention™ Duty Holster

Safariland Glock 17 Gen4 With TLR-1 Light Right Draw Holster

The 6360 ALS®/SLS Mid-ride duty holster is sturdy, lightweight, and provides an extra measure of security while on patrol. The ALS® (Automatic Locking System) builds on the foundation of the SLS (Self Locking System) to offer Level III Retention™. In addition to the SLS, Safariland's patented ALS locks the firearm into place immediately upon holstering, while the rotating hood and tension device ensure added security. The 6360 holster can be easily upgraded to Level IV Retention® using the optional Sentry attachment.

The 6360 ALS®/SLS Mid-ride is constructed of durable SafariLaminate™ and is lined with suede to protect the gun’s sights and finish. For a snug and comfortable fit, the mid-ride belt loop allows the holster to ride close to the body.

Product name: Smith & Wesson Universal Handcuff
Description:
LIMITED QUANTITY

The Smith & Wesson hinged universal handcuffs are ideal for both larger and smaller prisoners. The contoured shape of the swinging arm allows these handcuffs to open 25% wider and also close 25% smaller than standard Smith & Wesson handcuffs. Hinged handcuffs are used in applications where subject movement needs further restriction. The model 1 hinged handcuff uses the push pin double locking system. To double lock simply depress the double lock pin on the edge of the cuff with the back of your handcuff key. MEETS NIJ STANDARD 0307.01

Specifications:

  • Wrist Opening: 2.40
  • First Notch Inside Perimeter: 9.40
  • Last Notch Inside Perimeter: 5.80
  • Tightest Inside Width: 1.60
  • Weight: 12.0 oz
  • Locking Positions: 31
  • Distance Between Cuffs: 2.00
  • Maximum Overall Length: 9.85
  • Two Keys Included
